        <h1>Basic help concepts</h1>
        <p>This help file was created following basic concepts which, once understood, let you quickly consult file pages.</p>
        <h2>Organization</h2>
        <p class="Image">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/GuidaPrima parte.png" style="border: none;float: none;width: 450px;height: 370px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="450" height="370" border="0" />
        </p>
        <p>The help file includes an initial introduction section with chapters:</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
            <li class="p" value="1">
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Product introduction</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="2">
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Help introduction</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>And an operating section with chapters:</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
            <li class="p" value="1">
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">First start</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="2">
                <p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Procedures and FAQ</span>
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>A second more detailed part is included where setup and monitoring phases are described:</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
            <li class="p" value="1">
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Site configuration (physical setup)</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="2">
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Site configuration (logical setup)</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="3">
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">System setup</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="4">
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Monitoring the site</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>And an appendix with various technical information.</p>
